import React from 'react'
import {
    Switch,
    Route,
    useParams
} from "react-router-dom";
import { Comment, Contact, ContentData, Error, Useradmin, Home } from './'

export default function SwitchComp() {
    return (
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/">
                <Home />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/contentdatas">
                <ContentData />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/comments">
                <Comment />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/contacts">
                <Contact />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/useradmin">
                <Useradmin />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/errors/:id?">
                <Error />
            </Route>
        </Switch>
    )
}
